CHANGELOG.html.title: Change Log
CHANGELOG.html.body:
Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file. See standard-version for commit guidelines.
1.1.0 (2021-05-06)
Features

add new filter operators (distinct, takeWhile) (4cea2d8)
new reduce operators (reduce/reduceWith, scan/scanWith, every, some) (8692263)

Bug Fixes

fix curried typings and typos (c5c29e3)
